snippet.title: CIPHERCELL - Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo: https://game-genesis.itch.io/ciphercell-demo
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1527650/CIPHERCELL

CIPHERCELL is a minimalist logic puzzle game where you slide cells together to perform basic arithmetic, with the objective of getting last cell to zero.
